ckquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>輸哂未？<br />\n<br />\n打算輸幾多就收手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒左半年total 賺左3萬唔諗住收手</blockquote><br />\n1m半年先賺3萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家另外帳面賺緊萬幾<br />\n不過我知好撚少，出面有post話本金十幾萬要一年賺幾萬，或者每月要有10%回報，可能岩啲你地睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打 我本金同你差唔多<br />\n我係賺左17萬 唔係曬命<br />\n我舊年年頭開始買貨<br />\n果時恆指先18000定19000<br />\n純好運搭左順風車 <br />\n你就玩左半年<br />\n加上呢半年市場變化大<br />\n我覺得有賺已經算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我舊年年尾開始玩，高位接左貨所以計返賺得唔多"},{"pid":"8f97fd4271d059877d4864e3de0473ac53f9e9b3","tid":219074,"uid":37130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T11:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>輸哂未？<br />\n<br />\n打算輸幾多就收手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒左半年total 賺左3萬唔諗住收手</blockquote><br />\n1m半年先賺3萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家另外帳面賺緊萬幾<br />\n不過我知好撚少，出面有post話本金十幾萬要一年賺幾萬，或者每月要有10%回報，可能岩啲你地睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打如果你係呢半年先賺到 3%  咁你真係要小心熊市會hi 野</blockquote><br />\n其實唔係3%係三萬，因為唔係每次都all-in，有留資金等大調整吸平貨"},{"pid":"42b4cab3bcb49d11de7474a4555320e1f142e266","tid":219074,"uid":102198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:08:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>輸哂未？<br />\n<br />\n打算輸幾多就收手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒左半年total 賺左3萬唔諗住收手</blockquote><br />\n1m半年先賺3萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家另外帳面賺緊萬幾<