算輸幾多就收手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒左半年total 賺左3萬唔諗住收手</blockquote><br />\n1m半年先賺3萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家另外帳面賺緊萬幾<br />\n不過我知好撚少，出面有post話本金十幾萬要一年賺幾萬，或者每月要有10%回報，可能岩啲你地睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打如果你係呢半年先賺到 3%  咁你真係要小心熊市會hi 野</blockquote><br />\n其實唔係3%係三萬，因為唔係每次都all-in，有留資金等大調整吸平貨</blockquote><br />\n需要知道玩股票要順勢炒 大戶永遠快你一步 點解會出現平貨係因為大戶一早玩完隻股離左場 <br />\n<br />\n老散要記住一句就係妄想會擊退大戶</blockquote><br />\n點解釋700會由220跌到180又升返上去"},{"pid":"a1c3712131e8b6492a003f8881360f839e00b450","tid":219074,"uid":68993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一球，玩藍籌應該唔會死，長渣必勝</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買匯豐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買都買渣兜bank la</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係回樓主, 我係回佢個長渣必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n sor <br />\n<br />\n但真心advice 買渣兜都唔買HSBC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003cbec9db6320cb59bf8b3b7c06392741f5e708","tid":219074,"uid":68821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:30:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家幾成倉<br />\n組合分別有咩</blockquote><br />\n8成<br />\n941 @84.1<br />\n315 @10.22<br />\n1038 @62.8</blockquote><br />\n幾好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n資產分配學問比較難<br />\n而家大市處於上升浪 正常係賺錢 7-8成倉位合理<br />\n但到轉勢轉向下跌浪時 好少人會願意減倉 反而愈溝愈大<br />\n選股比較其次 樓主可以研究將一球分為幾份 進取股/防守股/收息股咁去玩 用一球咁去資產增值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925483a28103a89adc966b7daea8d6beb7d9d2cd","tid":219074,"uid":68993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:33:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家幾成倉<br />\n組合分別有咩</blockquote><br />\n8成<br />\n941 @84.1<br />\n315 @10.22<br />\n1038 @62.8</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解咁相信電訊股"},{"pid":"0e903e99eaccd92621e15934a31aaac1db570546","tid":219074,"uid":68821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家幾成倉<br />\n組合分別有咩</blockquote><br />\n8成<br />\n941 @84.1<br />\n315 @10.22<br />\n1038 @62.8</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解咁相信電訊股</blockquote><br />\n樓主投資定5G?"},{"pid":"c8bc51c9ca2f69bbff742549e11c0a7a789ce9ac","tid":219074,"uid":37130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家幾成倉<br />\n組合分別有咩</blockquote><br />\n8成<br />\n941 @84.1<br />\n315 @10.22<br />\n1038 @62.8</blockquote><br />\n幾好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n資產分配學問比較難<br />\n而家大市處於上升浪 正常係賺錢 7-8成倉位合理<br />\n但到轉勢轉向下跌浪時 好少人會願意減倉 反而愈溝愈大<br />\n選股比較其次 <span style=\"color: red;\">樓主可以研究將一球分為幾份 進取股/防守股/收息股咁去玩</span> 用一球咁去資產增值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個策略我未實踐到，收息股同防守股好多時簡埋同一隻，例如依家隻1038同941當收息，1038又可以防手。進取股到未識玩，睇開1137，美圖同IGG，但冇買入過。"},{"pid":"1396b81741b96ec95804744ff0b692b6fa400565","tid":219074,"uid":37130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:47:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家幾成倉<br />\n組合分別有咩</blockquote><br />\n8成<br />\n941 @84.1<br />\n315 @10.22<br />\n1038 @62.8</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解咁相信電訊股</blockquote><br />\n樓主投資定5G?</blockquote><br />\nYes, 中移就係搏中使用率上升。"}]}